  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "As dauntless knight Arthur you are caught up in the most dangerous of quests! A spell has been cast upon the kingdom. Your fair maiden, Princess Prin Prin has been snatched up by the evil emperor. Only as Arthur can you get her back from the creatures of the undead that haunt the land. Test your courage and skill to the limit. You must keep up the quest. On your journey, your mightiest weapon of all awaits you... MAGIC!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The main character, Knight Arthur utilizes a variety of weapons and a new action \"double jump\" to face formidable enemies and rescue the kidnapped princess.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
